%h3#api-objects-category Category

:markdown
  Categories are used to organize items in a menu. Categories can not be nested.

.row
  .span8
    %h4 Fields

    %dl
      %dt id :: integer
      %dd ID of the object.
      %dt name :: string
      %dd Name of the category.
      %dt position
      %dd
        :markdown
          Position of the category in menu. `null` if the category is disabled.
  .span8
    %h4 Example
    %pre
      = preserve do
        :escaped
          {
            "id": 18,
            "name": "Soft Drink",
            "position": 4,
          }


